OL,6,FA fifth person has been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with the deaths of two
OL,8,Fteenagers in Bristol.
OL,10,FA 26-year-old man was arrested
OL,11,Fovernight on suspicion of assisting an
OL,12,Foffender and is in police custody.
OL,14,FMax Dixon, 16, and Mason Rist, 15,
OL,15,Fwere both stabbed to death in an
OL,16,Fattack in Ilminster Avenue, in Knowle
OL,17,FWest, shortly after 11pm on Saturday
OL,18,F27 January.
