OL,6,FTwo people were initially arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder the following
OL,8,Fmorning, including a 44-year-old man
OL,9,Fand a 15-year-old.
OL,11,FThe 44-year-old remains in custody
OL,12,Fafter magistrates granted officers a
OL,13,Fwarrant of further detention while the
OL,14,F15-year-old has been bailed with
OL,15,Fconditions, including one to not enter
OL,16,FBristol.
OL,18,FOn Monday 29 January, two more men
OL,19,F(aged 20 and 22) were arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of murder.
