OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police
OL,7,FSuperintendent, Mark Runacres, said:
OL,8,F"The team investigating Mason Rist's
OL,9,Fand Max Dixon's deaths are working
OL,10,Faround the clock to bring those
OL,11,Fresponsible to justice.
OL,13,F"While they are only three days into
OL,14,Fthe inquiry, they have already
OL,15,Fcompleted a huge amount of work and
OL,16,Fthe inquiry is progressing rapidly.
OL,18,F"Already 253 exhibits have been
OL,19,Fseized, including weapons, while they
OL,20,Fhave also searched several properties.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
