OL,6,F"A dedicated team is also reviewing
OL,7,Fhundreds of hours of CCTV footage
OL,8,Fwhile specialist officers from
OL,9,Fneighbouring forces have also been
OL,10,Fbrought in to assist in order to
OL,11,Fensure no stone is left unturned.
OL,13,F"Everyone across the city has been
OL,14,Fshocked by what happened to Mason and
OL,15,FMax and our commitment to holding
OL,16,Fthose responsible to account will not
OL,17,Fwaiver.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
