OL,6,F"Family liaison officers continue to
OL,7,Fsupport Mason's and Max's family and
OL,8,Fare keeping them updated with
OL,9,Fdevelopments.
OL,11,F"There's been outpouring grief but
OL,12,Falso love and I know both families are
OL,13,Freally appreciative of the kindness
OL,14,Fshown to them at this difficult time.
OL,16,F"We are aware there is lots of
OL,17,Fspeculation, including online, about
OL,18,Fwhat took place and it's difficult to
OL,19,Fcomprehend what has motivated people
OL,20,Fto carry out such a reprehensible
OL,21,Fattack. It's senseless.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
