OL,6,F"However, it's important we keep an
OL,7,Fopen mind and let the Major Crime
OL,8,FInvestigation Team carry out their
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"The arrests reflect that we are
OL,12,Fbuilding a full picture of what
OL,13,Fhappened and I hope it is only a
OL,14,Fmatter of time before we are able to
OL,15,Fprovide Mason's and Max's families
OL,16,Fwith the answers they deserve."
