OL,6,FHe added: "We have officers across
OL,7,FSouth Bristol and we're committed to
OL,8,Fsupporting people deal with this
OL,9,Fhorrific incident but also with any
OL,10,Fconcerns they may have in the weeks
OL,11,Fand months ahead.
OL,13,F"The Neighbourhood Policing teams have
OL,14,Fworked hard over the past few years
OL,15,Facross the city to help young people
OL,16,Fmake better life choices and deter
OL,17,Fthem away from crime and anti-social
OL,18,Fbehaviour and they will continue to do
OL,19,Fthis.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
