OL,6,F"In addition to this engagement work,
OL,7,Fwe also effectively use our powers
OL,8,Funder the Anti-Social Behaviour Act to
OL,9,Fissue injunctions, anti-social
OL,10,Fbehaviour contracts and criminal
OL,11,Fbehaviour orders to manage people who
OL,12,Fare causing harm to our communities."
